    <title>How to Use This Reference</title>
    <para> The &RESTAPI; is the interface that enables you to interact with the &PRODUCTABBR; Secure
        Data Service. This reference lists the API resources that developers need when forming the
        URIs in their REST API calls. </para>
    <para>
        Each resource listing includes the following information:
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                A description of the resource and its context
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                The URI path
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Request body and response code information for each
                method
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para> Links to relevant schema documentation (for the Secure Data Service URIs) </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Resource-specific fields and parameters
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Links to examples
            </para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <para> See the &PRODUCTABBR; developer documentation at <link
            xlink:href="https://www.inbloom.org/developer-documentation"
            >inbloom.org/developer-documentaion</link> for more details about the REST API itself
        and how to develop applications that use API calls, including: </para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Example usage scenarios
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                URI patterns with examples
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Media types
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Global parameters
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Query operators
            </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>
                Authentication and authorization
            </para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
</chapter>
